      <h1 class='title'>Government Chemist</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 03 June 2003 vol 406 cc2-3WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_2ws' title='Col. 2WS &mdash; HC Deb 03 June 2003 vol 406 c2WS' name='column_2ws' href='#column_2ws' rel='bookmark'>2WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0406P0_20030603_CWS_3'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-patricia-hewitt' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0406P0_20030603_CWS_3' title='Link to this speech by Ms Patricia Hewitt' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-patricia-hewitt" title="Ms Patricia Hewitt">The Secretary of State for Trade and Industry (Ms Patricia Hewitt)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">I have just received the sixth annual Review of the Government Chemist and I am arranging
          <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_3ws' title='Col. 3WS &mdash; HC Deb 03 June 2003 vol 406 c3WS' name='column_3ws' href='#column_3ws' rel='bookmark'>3WS</a>
          for copies to be placed in the Libraries of both Houses plus those of the devolved administrations in Scotland, Wales and Northern Ireland.</p>
        </blockquote>
